Just as you can’t imagine Christmas without cake & wine; wine-making has to be paired with some traditional grape-treading or stomping! For the first time in Calicut, The Raviz Kadavu invites you to a ‘Grape Stomping Ceremony’ co-sponsored by Grover Wines. The exciting event will be followed by poolside brunch, fun-filled activities & flea market. Get those tootsies moving!  Rate: INR 1500+Taxes/Adults
INR 750+Taxes/Children(5 to 12 years)

For more information:
Email: fnb.kadavu@theraviz.com
Toll-Free: 1800 4252 2220| www.theraviz.com
